I"<p>This weekend, the <a href="http://www.idmil.org/mg3">third conference on music and gesture</a> will take place in Montreal this coming Friday and Saturday. Marcin Swoboda and I will be presenting on <em>Encoding emotion: how performers manipulate tempo locally to convey affect</em>.</p>

<p>The conference forms part of the <a href="http://www.music.mcgill.ca/musimars/mm2010/theme.html">musimars music festival</a>, organized this year under the theme ‘gestural music–musical gesture.’ All throughout this week, there will be concerts and lectures at the <a href="http://www.mcgill.ca/music/">Schulich School of Music</a>.</p>

